[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    369[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      - billing_inquiry_route                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    370[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    371[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Scope discipline]                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    372[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Within-scope: scheduling, rescheduling, referral     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    373[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      tracking, care-plan task surfacing, benefits         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    374[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      navigation, message routing, transportation,         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    375[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      social-care navigation, transitions-of-care          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    376[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      orchestration                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    377[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Outside-scope (route appropriately): clinical        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    378[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      advice, medication adjustment, test interpretation,  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    379[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      diagnosis, prior-authorization clinical content,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    380[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      mental-health crisis (route to recipe 11.8           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    381[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pathway), active medical emergency                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    382[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    383[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Action-confirmation discipline]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    384[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - High-impact actions (scheduling, rescheduling,       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    385[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      sending messages on the patient's behalf) require    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    386[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      explicit confirmation                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    387[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Low-impact actions (lookups) do not                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    388[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient can configure preference                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    389[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    390[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Citation discipline]                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    391[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Every cross-system fact grounded in a tool call      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    392[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - No fabricated referral status, no fabricated         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    393[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      appointment times                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    394[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    395[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    396[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: composed response with cited tool-call         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    397[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    results, action proposals, escalation recommendations] │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    398[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    399[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    400[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    401[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── OUTPUT SAFETY + ACTION-CONFIRMATION ───────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    402[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    403[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard output safety primitives from recipe 11.1]    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    404[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scope filter (no clinical advice; no medication      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    405[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      recommendations; no test interpretation)             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    406[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Vendor-managed guardrail layer                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    407[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    408[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Coordination-specific verification]                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    409[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-system facts grounded in tool calls            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    410[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Action proposals correctly formatted with target     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    411[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      system, parameters, and reversibility               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    412[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - High-impact actions have explicit confirmation flow  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    413[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Low-impact actions can proceed                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    414[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Action proposals respect family-caregiver scope      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    415[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      where applicable                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    416[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    417[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    418[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: response cleared for delivery; pending action  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    419[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    queue; escalation events]                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    420[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    421[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    422[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    423[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ACTION EXECUTION + WARM HANDOFF ───────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    424[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    425[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Action execution within authorized scope]              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    426[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Schedule appointment                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    427[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Reschedule appointment                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    428[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Send non-clinical message to clinician (with         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    429[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      structured context)                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    430[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Send message to care-coordinator                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    431[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Request refill (routed through pharmacy workflow)    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    432[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Request transportation                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    433[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Request social-care referral                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    434[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Mark care-plan task complete (for tasks the bot can  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    435[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      verify completion of)                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    436[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    437[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Warm-handoff triggers]                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    438[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis screen positive (handoff to recipe 11.8       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    439[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pathway)                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    440[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Out-of-scope clinical question                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    441[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient distress at care burden                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    442[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Caregiver burden                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    443[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sustained-trajectory pattern of missed coordination  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    444[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      tasks                                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    445[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Social-determinants barrier requiring care-          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    446[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      management                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    447[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient explicit request for human                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    448[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot confidence below threshold                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    449[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - End-of-life transition or bereavement signal         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    450[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    451[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Handoff targets]                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    452[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-coordinator (institution's RN-or-equivalent     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    453[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      workforce)                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    454[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-management program (for elevated-risk routing)  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    455[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Social-care navigation                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    456[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient's PCP or specialty team                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    457[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis pathway (for mental-health crisis)            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    458[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bereavement support (for bereavement signals)        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    459[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    460[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Bridge-and-stay pattern]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    461[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot bridges to human within the platform             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    462[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot stays present until human has joined where       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    463[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      situation calls for synchronous bridge               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    464[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - For asynchronous handoffs, bot confirms the          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    465[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      handoff was received and provides expected timeline  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    466[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    467[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    468[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: action-execution confirmation; handoff event   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    469[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    with structured payload to appropriate target]         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    470[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    471[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
